Ranger Help for: carve arrow
=============================

SYNTAX:      make arrow
             make bolt
             carve arrow
             carve bolt
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to carve arrows or crossbow bolts from wood.
Arrows are used with shortbows and longbows. Bolts are used with
crossbows and are required for heartshot.

Ammo can be improved with flame arrow, poison arrow, and tip arrow. The
same commands can be used on bolts when preparing crossbow ammunition.
